show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/qCWwCP
show.description:
A boxing champion’s world collides with a struggling florist when fate traps them in a contract neither wanted.
As betrayal, humiliation, and hidden conspiracies rise, love sparks in the unlikeliest of places.
But when duty clashes with desire, the question remains—will sacrifice or survival win?
